h3. Problem

There are multiple links missing on [Tutorial: Bamboo Specs YAML stored in Bitbucket Server \- Atlassian Documentation|https://confluence.atlassian.com/bamboo/tutorial-bamboo-specs-yaml-stored-in-bitbucket-server-941616819.html]

Examples:
{quote}
Step 4: Create Bamboo Specs project using Maven
...
2 Use any of the templates LINK TO TEMPLATES or write YAML definition on your own LINK TO YAML format.
{quote}

{quote}
Next steps
...
LINK TO Bamboo Specs YAML reference. 
{quote}

There is also a wrong formatting in (line feed)
{quote}
Step 3: Enable processing of Bamboo Specs in your repository
Go to  > Linked repositories. 
{quote}

